psidev.psi.mi.jami.enricher

Interface OrganismEnricher

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MIEnricher<Organism>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FullOrganismEnricher, FullOrganismUpdater, MinimalOrganismEnricher, MinimalOrganismUpdater

    public interface OrganismEnricher
extends MIEnricher<Organism>
    An organism enricher which can enrich either a single organism or a collection. The organismEnricher has CvTermEnricher as sub enrichers subEnrichers.
    Since:
    22/05/13
    Author:
    Gabriel Aldam (galdam@ebi.ac.uk)
